name: Instinct
summary: Instinct is an abstract-arcade-puzzle shooter that tests your cognition and hand eye coordination with a small emphasis on strategizing under pressure.  The game is easy to play, all you have to do is hit the right shape with the right button. In Casual mode you have the Button hints enabled while Hard mode removes those hints for added challenge. Chain combos to get more points. Strategize to get the best possible score. Each target counts, each second counts.
